TornadoBB is a Simple & Fast Forum based on Tornado Frameworks written by Python and mongoDB

Features:

-- fast and lightweight
-- easy to install and config
-- easy to extend functions
-- basic functions as a forum
-- UI from fluxbb
-- multi CSS styles
-- i18n support 
-- simple code
-- perfect for the user who own youself server or VPS

Requirement:

-- python 2.6 or above
-- tornado web framework
-- mongoDB
-- pytz
-- pygments
-- postmarkup
